item.title: New God of War III Scans
item.dc:creator: Inou
item.description:
Showing to the people how well the development is, they said it that the game is much nicer than Uncharted 2 now… and the game is released 9 months after the E3 demo, so we can expect that it is gonna be different…

BTW, I just bought God of War Collection today! I tried the E3 demo, and it’s awesome! The only thing that I dislike in the demo is that the difficulty cannot be set and is on Easy… But anyway, you fucking pull Helios’ head off with your bare hands! WITH YOUR BARE HANDS!!! :freeman:
